{"tid":2067890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[勵志post] 無力感重嘅巴打入黎睇睇，呢個人面對緊咁多野都未放棄同無力，我地更加冇放棄嘅理由","createTime":"2020-06-17T09:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T15:54:26.000Z","uid":31215,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c829661495fb4fac77d90ff02034bdba25268d88","tid":2067890,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T09:50:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2020/01/p8948321a537625675-800x450.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2Fp8948321a537625675-800x450.jpg&h=de8a8dc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中印衝突<br />\n香港示威<br />\n台灣冇武統以外嘅可能性<br />\n三峽大壩變型<br />\n蝗蟲<br />\n水災<br />\n爆炸<br />\n北京肺炎<br />\n武肺責任追究<br />\n失業率<br />\n6億人月入少過1000<br />\n外資同生產線撤緊<br />\n南海衝突<br />\n美國吹雞D奶共盟友都走哂，而且準備搞9自己<br />\n部署多年嘅華為俾人退5G，而家晶片軟件都冇電話都做唔成<br />\n孟晚舟救唔返，殺佢又殺唔到，分分鐘爆大鑊<br />\n共產黨內部壓力<br />\n<br />\n牙習都未無力<br />\n我地都唔好無力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c0494ff650306b30330a8c9a9fa899324435a43","tid":2067890,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T09:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fffe790831289458671ac6eb4d1b0fc3155c8cbb","tid":2067890,"uid":229502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T09:52:08.000Z","msg":"啊屎大大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc7c07eda94666bcacc259cfd81d93c9110ba40","tid":2067890,"uid":31215,"like"